<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV33">
<l>aruḷār tiruccak karattā lakalvicum punilaṉu</l>
<l>miruḷār viṉaikeṭac ceṅkōl naṭāvuti rīṅkōrpeṇpāṟ</l>
<l>poruḷō veṉumikaḻ vōvivaṟ ṟiṉpuṟat tāḷeṉṟeṇṇō</l>
<l>teruḷō maravaṇai yīrivaḷ māmai citaikkiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With [your] gracious brilliant discus you conduct just rule over wide heaven and earth,</l>
<l>so that Karma filled with darkness gets lost. Is it contempt:</l>
<l>“one woman’s fate here, [has it] meaning?” or is it calculation: “she’s outside these”?</l>
<l>We don’t understand, you on the serpent bed. Her dark colour is spoilt.</l>
<l></l>
<l>b</l>
<l>in one woman here, is there something valuable?</l>
<l></l>
<l>c</l>
<l>[You are] spoiling her darkness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
